summary: The example I made in my tutorial on making puzzle pillars, uploaded so that people can see how it works.
descriptionHtml:
I made a tutorial on how to create puzzle pillars using the Creation Kit, and it was requested that I upload the file I showed in the video so that people could download and view it. The purpose of this file is simply to be viewed in the creation kit so that it can be seen how puzzle pillars work, though if you wish to view this in game then the cell id is \"puzzlepillartut\". 
The video of my tutorial can be found here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OJbQeTviRzE&feature=plcp&context=C30fee3eUDOEgsToPDskJcYPxIner_cCFilJumQo1I
author: starbucksisevil
